underlying_goal: To test and fix the "cloud storage system" (problem 2) to ensure it is fully implemented and correct.
primary_success: Proactively created a comprehensive test runner from JSON test cases, which surfaced three subtle bugs that the original tests missed, and then fixed all of them.
brief_summary: Tasked with verifying an implementation, Claude went beyond the existing tests by creating a new test runner from JSON specs. This revealed three bugs (related to user capacity, admin creation, and compressed file naming), all of which Claude successfully fixed. Claude also corrected an outdated test case, resulting in a fully verified solution.
